snippet.title: Sea of Thieves Season 14: Unlockable Cosmetics
snippet.description:
Whether you like the look of the Shadow Tide gear earned by raising Renown or the Inner Sanctum items that lead the purchasable Plunder Pass, all the cosmetics you see here are available to pirates who sneak about during Season 14!

----------------------------------------

Buy the game and forge your own legend: https://www.seaofthieves.com/buy 
Dive into the Sea of Thieves Forums: https://www.seaofthieves.com/forum 
Stay updated with the Sea of Thieves WhatsApp Broadcast Channel: https://aka.ms/SoTWhatsApp
Follow Sea of Thieves on Twitter: https://aka.ms/SoTTwitter 
Live your best pirate's life with us on TikTok: https://aka.ms/SoTTikTok
Watch live Sea of Thieves piracy on Twitch: https://aka.ms/SoTTwitch
Soak up Sea of Thieves sunsets on Instagram: https://aka.ms/SoTInsta
Like Sea of Thieves on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/SeaOfThievesGame
Talk Sea of Thieves on Discord: https://aka.ms/SoTDiscord
For anything else, go to: https://www.seaofthieves.com
